                    <span>I have read machine learning writed by Tom M. Mitchell and also I have read Data Mining Concepts and Techniques writed by J. Han and M. Kamber. Both text books is very useful for someone who want to get concept of a modern data analysis approaches. But, however, to understant about that clearly, you should read this book also because the example and author's form writing is so good and nice, very easy to understant.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Disappointing</div>
